    <div style="padding-left: 10px;">
      <i class="fa fa-quote-left" aria-hidden="true"></i><br>
      <div style="padding-left: 20px; font-weight: 200; font-size: 20px; font-family: 'PT Sans', sans-serif;">
        Away is a place where it is not about the money you spend, 
